EU’s Rehn Says Commission Is Working on Report on Euro Bonds

-- B y   K a t i   P o h j a n p a l o
-- 
2011-10-07T07:50:46Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-07/eu-s-rehn-says-commission-is-working-on-report-on-euro-bonds.html
The European Commission is working on
a report exploring a range of options on how common euro bonds
can be introduced in the region, European Union Economic
Commissioner Olli Rehn said in a speech in Helsinki today. The
report will include “several options,” Rehn said, without
elaborating.  To contact the reporter on this story:
